  "prompt": "How do you pre-select a seat when booking a flight on Royal Air Maroc?",
  "response": "When booking a flight on Royal Air Maroc, you can pre-select your seat through their official website or by contacting their customer service. Here\u2019s a step-by-step guide on how to do it online:\n\n### **Via Royal Air Maroc\u2019s Website:**\n1. **Visit the Official Website**: Go to [Royal Air Maroc\u2019s website](https://www.royalairmaroc.com).\n2. **Book Your Flight**: Enter your travel details and proceed with the booking process until you reach the payment section.\n3. **Select Your Seat**:\n   - Before finalizing your payment, you\u2019ll be given the option to choose your seat.\n   - A seat map will appear, showing available seats. You can select your preferred seat (e.g., window, aisle, or extra legroom) based on availability and any applicable fees.\n4. **Complete Your Booking**: After selecting your seat, proceed to payment to confirm your reservation.\n\n### **Via Manage My Booking:**\nIf you\u2019ve already booked your flight but didn\u2019t select a seat initially, you can still pre-select one:\n1. **Log into Your Account**: Go to the Royal Air Maroc website and log into your account.\n2. **Access Your Booking**: Navigate to the \u201cManage My Booking\u201d section.\n3. **Select Your Seat**: Review your itinerary and choose your seat from the available options.\n4. **Confirm Your Selection**: Save your seat choice.\n\n### **Additional Notes**:\n- **Fees**: Depending on your fare class and seat selection, there may be additional charges for certain seats (e.g., extra legroom or premium seats).\n- **Availability**: Seat pre-selection is subject to availability. If you\u2019re unable to select a seat online, you may be able to do so at check-in.\n- **Contact Customer Service**: If you encounter any issues, you can reach out to Royal Air Maroc\u2019s customer service for assistance.\n\nBy pre-selecting your seat, you can ensure a more comfortable and tailored travel experience.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
